official_title: Personality and Cancer Care Study: Examining the Effects of a Personality Feedback Intervention in Adults With Cancer
inclusion_criteria:
* consent to participate
* at least 18 years old (self-reported)
* have a current or past cancer diagnosis (self-reported)
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* under 18 years old (self-reported)
* indicate that they have no known history of cancer (self-reported)
* unable to read or understand English
